# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Unreal Engine — generated / build output. NEVER commit these; they are
# regenerated locally and are huge. (Source/, Content/, Config/ and the
# .uproject ARE committed — see below.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Build + intermediate output (regenerated on compile)
Binaries/
Build/
Intermediate/
DerivedDataCache/

# Local-only editor state (autosaves, logs, per-user prefs, PIE temp)
Saved/
Backup/

# IDE / project files — regenerated via "Generate Visual Studio project files"
.vs/
.idea/
*.sln
*.sdf
*.opensdf
*.suo
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.xcodeproj
*.xcworkspace

# Cesium for Unreal local request cache (per-machine, not shared)
cesium-request-cache.sqlite
cesium-request-cache.sqlite-shm
cesium-request-cache.sqlite-wal

# Misc
UpgradeLog.htm
*.log
